/* REMOVED: the metric-adjusted local() fallback faces ("Geist Sans Fallback",
   "JetBrains Mono Fallback"). Chrome can match a local()+size-adjust face and
   then fail glyph loading, falling to the LAST-RESORT font (Times) instead of
   the next family in the stack: observed live as Rendered Fonts "Times-Bold,
   Local file" despite a valid sans stack. The token stacks now fall back to
   plain system sans/mono faces directly. Do not reintroduce metric-override
   local() faces without testing Rendered Fonts in Chrome. */
